Short Interest In Bank of Hawaii Moves 13% Lower
The most recent short interest data has been released by the NASDAQ for the 09/30/2015 settlement date, which shows a 509,389 share decrease in total short interest for Bank of Hawaii Corp , to 3,395,739, a decrease of 13.04% since 09/15/2015. Total short interest is just one way to look at short data; another metric that we here at Dividend Channel find particularly useful is the "days to cover" metric because it considers both the total shares short and the average daily volume of shares traded.

